	* gtk/gtkctree.c (draw_row): added new "line style"
	GTK_CTREE_LINES_TABBED 
	* gtk/gtkctree.c/h (gtk_ctree_find_glist_ptr): new function to
	search the glist pointer of an GtkCTreeRow

