	environment to genmarshal.pl.
	(gtk.defs,gtktypebuiltins*): Add $(srcdir) where needed (in the
	rule), and removed it where not needed (in the dependencies).

	* gtk/genmarshal.pl: Look for `gtkmarshal.list' in $srcdir.

